For the collaboration, we chose each other because we believe in humanity, in globalization and most of all we believe in love. 
Don t let a bunch of people tell us once again that we have to hate each other for no reason.

We are very proud that Nirvana, not because of the collaboration, but thank to her talent, has been noticed by Forbes that has recently published a nice interview.
